title: The Contessa's Secret (1954 History) Yvonne De Carlo: Romance & Royal Deception

sources.title: The Contessa's Secret (1954 History) Yvonne De Carlo: Romance & Royal Deception
sources.description:
The Countess of Castiglione, who wishes Italian unity, saves a young patriot, Falengo, at the time of a murder attempt on Victor- Emmanuel II.

Original title: La Contessa di Castiglione

Director: Georges Combret
Writers : Claude Boissol, Georges Combret, Leonardo Magagnini
Actors: Yvonne De Carlo, Georges Marchal, Paul Meurisse

Genres: Drama, History, Romance
Release date: September 27, 1954 (France)
